_struct_biol.id        1 
_struct_biol.details   
;The biological unit is a tetramer. The following symmetry operation is required to build the tetramer from the dimer in the asymmetric unit: 
 
rotation matrix: 
-1 0 0 
 0 1 0 
 0 0 -1 
 
translation vector: 
234.72900    0.00000    0.00000 
 
The equivalent Eulerean rotation is 
 Phi =   0.00000, Theta = 180.00000, Psi =   0.00000
